        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Murray has been enrolled in F.O.S. for some time now, this college is his best chance to establish connections with leaders of Babylonia.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 58,
        "ActionId": 58,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'He does not have the advantage of a good family background. If he wants to make it into the inner circle of Babylonia as quickly as possible, then he has no time to waste and will have to utilize all the resources available to him.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 59,
        "ActionId": 59,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'All will go according to his plan, he will get to his desired position without attracting much attention. Then he will be able to protect Morian from up there and his brother will not even know about it.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 60,
        "ActionId": 60,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: '—This was his \"ridiculous plan\" that he formed when he was young and naive.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 61,
        "ActionId": 61,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But for now, he is no different than his classmates who enthusiastically talk about Construct soldiers, he can only stand on the side and watch.'}"
    },
    {
